==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whip-tom-kelly
<hw>Whip"-tom`-kel"ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[So called
in imitation of its notes.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A vireo
(<spn>Vireo altiloquus</spn>) native of the West Indies and Florida; --
called also <altname>black-whiskered vireo</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whipworm</ent>⟦br⟧
